items.headline: Welcome to the Everyman HYBRID Wiki!
items.desc: EverymanHYBRID is an online transmedia story that began as an amateur YouTube fitness series in March 2010. The series features three guys in their 20s named Vincent, Evan, and Jeff. A familiar entity may be found lingering in the videos as a horrific easter-egg: the tall, eldritch Slenderman. What at first seemed a contrived "Slenderman rip-off series" spiraled, looped and flashed back to become something much, much worse; something truly awful. Join our wiki to find out more.
